TypeDefinition

Authors

Crashdome

Description

Abstract Class. Helper that provides lookup and retrieval of global static enumerations.  Derived classes created with XPS_fnc_createEnumeration will store a type-safe set of enumeration references to global variables which are constants (compileFinal'd).  Additionally, it will create a static helper class using this definition.

See <XPS_fnc_createEnumeration> for more info on usage of types inheriting this type
